node.text: Having Hammerhead as a partner has been a game-changer in working my way back to the Tour de France.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Chris Froome on July 18, 2021 tagging @noa_toledo_arnonphoto, @sciconsports, @hammerheadrides, and @teamisraelsun. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text:
It’s been a bumpy road but we’re almost in Paris! 😁
Thank you so much for the amazing support over the last 3 weeks, it has meant so much to me 💛
#stage21 #TDF2021

#TDF2021

node.text:
#stage9 started out okay then it went a bit sideways 🤪 Thanks to everyone who tried to help. Just another character building day on @letourdefrance 🤣💛 #TDF2021 (part of my adventurous day was captured by a fan in my stories)
Getting all my bad luck out the way before next year 🤞🍀
📸 @noa_toledo_arnonphoto
